<title>UK: London gold fixes firmer, boosted by PGM strength.</title>
<headline>London gold fixes firmer, boosted by PGM strength.</headline>
<text>
<p>GOLD - Fixes at $343.80 versus $340.80 on Thursday PM. Firmer within recent range, assisted by rocketing PGMs.</p>
<p>SILVER - Also stronger at $4.92/$4.96, versus $4.79/$4.81.</p>
<p>PLATINUM - Trading at seven-year highs, fixes at $495.00, versus $442.00. Extremely volatile.</p>
<p>PALLADIUM - Fixes at $240.00 versus $210.00, hits fresh 17-year highs.</p>
</text>
